.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/190542_e984bbaeb7facec92e95583f06916156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F190542_e984bbaeb7facec92e95583f06916156.jpg&h=b5095944&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\niPhone 咁on dog dog gar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn dog dog想法咪要用on dog dog方法<br />\nAndroid可以有人打電話過黎果陣有鈴聲，WhatsApp就淨係震？</blockquote><br />\n緊係得<br />\n有電話入係響<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whatsapp individual 只震不響</span><br />\nWhatsapp group 不震不響<br />\n呢個setting用左6年<br />\n<br />\n轉左iphone之後，點set 都set 唔返呢個setting, 問fd 先知原來要要同call同步，call響 whatsapp 就可以響，要whatsapp 唔響，電話都唔可以響</blockquote><br />\n一樣 轉左iphone之後好耐先習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7814dd79d7daace82440335b4345bb0366f9b5","tid":366773,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入段冇聲嘅鈴聲落iPhone <br />\n去呢到改成嗰個冇聲鈴聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/190542_e984bbaeb7facec92e95583f06916156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F190542_e984bbaeb7facec92e95583f06916156.jpg&h=b5095944&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\niPhone 咁on dog dog gar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn dog dog想法咪要用on dog dog方法<br />\nAndroid可以有人打電話過黎果陣有鈴聲，WhatsApp就淨係震？</blockquote><br />\nAndroid可以"},{"pid":"d9a53308be2b59aa25639f5be1282fb68ebcdf7b","tid":366773,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入段冇聲嘅鈴聲落iPhone <br />\n去呢到改成嗰個冇聲鈴聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/190542_e984bbaeb7facec92e95583f06916156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F